name: Impresion Abstracta 1 / Abstract Impression 1
description: This is my first NFT, In this work I wanted to recreate myself in impressionism but in an abstract way, I played with the colors and spots that the impressionists used in their palette without trying to give it any more shape without movement. The work exists in physical form, in acrylic on canvas, the measurements are: 120 cm x 90 cm.
